{"tid":2396083,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"譚杏藍自爆多段被性侵經歷　勉勵受害人發聲：唔可以縱容加害者","createTime":"2021-02-05T10:14:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-10T12:34:48.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8d4a19f29b42b82d4eeda7fdc672a11999a7160d","tid":2396083,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T10:14:57.000Z","msg":"譚杏藍（小花）昨日（5/2）在YouTube頻道公開一條短片大談在學期間多段被性侵犯的經歷，當中更有一次是慘遭迎面而來的陌生男子揸下體：「可能嗰啲人之後會大大聲同人炫耀，或者自己喺度爽，不論男女都好，我都想帶出正確觀念，一定要企出嚟，為自己發聲，呢樣嘢非常緊要，唔可以縱容加害者。」<br />\n<br />\n片段出街後，亦有不少女性向小花分享被性騷擾、性侵犯的經歷，她接受傳媒訪問時指出，今次拍片的目的便是讓觀眾不應覺得類似經歷普遍而最終決定啞忍，又指現在的自己比起之前「辣」很多，眼前發生類似事件，必定會挺身而出。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210205/434380545478103040704169.jpeg/1QY4ztszZybASobTTr-buOxhL-KM5p0afg_iyn4P4so?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210205%2F434380545478103040704169.jpeg%2F1QY4ztszZybASobTTr-buOxhL-KM5p0afg_iyn4P4so%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=8d4160b0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210205/434380547743158272568940.jpeg/62zSZa949JKmc9GXffouuf7Qjr5tkPC4ekqY0npKmNI?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210205%2F434380547743158272568940.jpeg%2F62zSZa949JKmc9GXffouuf7Qjr5tkPC4ekqY0npKmNI%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=8b8e721a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a64bce05333c18481999853e65b586c8fa2ca4b1","tid":2396083,"uid":95520,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T10:15:49.000Z","msg":"咁撚樣衰<br />\n邊個咁得閒侵犯"},{"pid":"4b1857fd630cc06cd521c7678e08810a5e7d28e1","tid":2396083,"uid":271397,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T10:16:20.000Z","msg":"好開針牙我比人搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52a07a542ab401aba62cc141a555ace73a2ea623","tid":2396083,"uid":14131,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a64bce05333c18481999853e65b586c8fa2ca4b1","tid":